episodes.title: Kiefer reacts to town's mention in Epstein investigation files
episodes.description:
Newly released federal documents related to the Jeffrey Epstein investigation have unexpectedly drawn attention to the small town of Kiefer, located about 25 minutes south of Tulsa.

Read the story: https://okcfox.com/news/local/kiefer-reacts-to-towns-mention-in-epstein-investigation-files-jeffrey-justice-department-donald-trump-president-administration-oklahoma-tulsa-documents-federal-investigation
